JSON Array to LabVIEW Array Base Type.vi

This VI takes a JSON Node (all types besides JSON Object) and assigns the value to the LabVIEW Base Type of compatible reference.

If the LabVIEW base type is an array of boolean, numeric, or string this function will attempt to check if a JSON Array type will map
